What is Tap2Pay?
            
            Tap2Pay is a free digital wallet that 
securely  stores  your  credit  cards,  debit
cards,  the gift  cards, loyalty cards,  offers, 
and more.  With  Tap2Pay, you can shop in
stores, buy online, and send money.
            
Send Money:

            You can send or request money to 
anyone in the  U.S. with an email  account 
through Gmail or the Tap2Pay app. If  they 
don’t  have a  Tap2Pay already, they can it
create one  in  order  to  send and receive
money.

